      "acceptanceCriteria": "Richardson extrapolation or equivalent applied to all QoIs; discretization error bounds reported with confidence intervals.",
      "rationale": "Richardson extrapolation applied to pressure rise and flow rate QoIs. Hemolysis index discretization error not rigorously bounded. Achieved level 3 versus required 4."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
