      "acceptanceCriteria": "Experimental test conditions fully characterized and traceable to COU operating envelope with uncertainty quantification.",
      "rationale": "FDA pump test conditions documented at nominal operating point only. Off-design and patient-variability conditions not characterized. Significant gap relative to MRL 5 requirement."
